    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="search">Search</h1><p>Search features are enabled by default, but requires a few steps to make it available.</p><ol type="1"><li>Run</li></ol><div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre class="sourceCode sh"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb1-1"><a href="#cb1-1" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="co"># [hexo-generator-search](https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-generator-search)</span></span><span id="cb1-2"><a href="#cb1-2" aria-hidden="true"></a>$ <span class="ex">npm</span> install hexo-generator-search --save</span></code></pre></div><ol start="2" type="1"><li>Add these lines to blog configuration <code>_config.yml</code>:</li></ol><div class="sourceCode" id="cb2"><pre class="sourceCode yml"><code class="sourceCode yaml"><span id="cb2-1"><a href="#cb2-1" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="fu">search</span><span class="kw">:</span></span><span id="cb2-2"><a href="#cb2-2" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="at">  </span><span class="fu">path</span><span class="kw">:</span><span class="at"> search.json</span></span><span id="cb2-3"><a href="#cb2-3" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="at">  </span><span class="fu">content</span><span class="kw">:</span><span class="at"> </span><span class="ch">false</span></span></code></pre></div><ol start="3" type="1"><li>Add new search page so that Hexo will generate it.</li></ol><div class="sourceCode" id="cb3"><pre class="sourceCode sh"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb3-1"><a href="#cb3-1" aria-hidden="true"></a>$ <span class="ex">hexo</span> new page <span class="st">&#39;search&#39;</span></span></code></pre></div><ol start="4" type="1"><li>Replace all its content with:</li></ol><div class="sourceCode" id="cb4"><pre class="sourceCode markdown"><code class="sourceCode markdown"><span id="cb4-1"><a href="#cb4-1" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="co">---</span></span><span id="cb4-2"><a href="#cb4-2" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="an">type:</span><span class="co"> search</span></span><span id="cb4-3"><a href="#cb4-3" aria-hidden="true"></a><span class="co">---</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Done! Your search page is ready at <code>/search/</code>.</p>]]></content>
